    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I was writing a unit test for my application using Zend_Http_Client-&gt;setParameterPost().
When launching the test I get a PHP warning:</p>

<p>Warning: http_build_query() expects at most 2 parameters, 3 given in {path_to_my_app}\include\zf\library\Zend\Http\Client.php on line 935</p>

<p>In fact, looking at that line there is:
$body = http_build_query($this-&gt;paramsPost, '', '&amp;');</p>

<p>Thanks</p>

